@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_meoakh(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v1 = wp.exp(tmp)
    v0 = (((tmp + 0.15 * v2 + 0.79) * (tmp + 0.14 / v2 + 0.92)) + (v0 - wp.sin(tmp + 0.68)))
    tmp = (wp.cos(v0) - wp.sin((v1 + 0.99 / tmp + 0.03)))
    tmp = 0.95
    v2 = (0.15 * v2)
    v0 = (0.81 * ((v2 + 0.07 / v2 + 0.05) - (tmp + 0.01 + v2 + 0.11)))
    data[tid] = v0
